---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="The Second Spring – Perimenopause Support for Indian Women"
  description="India's first private companion for women navigating perimenopause. Ask anything, understand what's happening, and find real support — in a language that feels like home."
>

  <!-- ── HERO ── -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg-shapes">
      <div class="shape shape-1"></div>
      <div class="shape shape-2"></div>
      <div class="shape shape-3"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="eyebrow">🌸 India's perimenopause companion</div>
        <h1>
          You're not going mad.<br/>
          <em>Your body is changing.</em>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-desc">
          Mood swings, sleepless nights, brain fog, hot flashes — and everyone around you says
          "it's just stress" or "you're getting older." You deserve more than that.
          The Second Spring is a safe, private space to finally understand what's happening.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="/chat" class="btn btn-peach btn-lg">Start a private conversation →</a>
          <a href="#about" class="btn btn-outline-white">Our story</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-trust">
          <span>✦ Anonymous &amp; private</span>
          <span>✦ No login required</span>
          <span>✦ Indian women understood here</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── STATS STRIP ── -->
  <div class="stats-strip">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats-row">
        {[
          { num: '46.2', unit: 'yrs', label: 'Average menopause age for Indian women — earlier than most expect' },
          { num: '30M+', unit: '', label: 'Indian women entering this transition every year' },
          { num: '8–10', unit: 'yrs', label: 'How long perimenopause can last before menopause arrives' },
          { num: '<30%', unit: '', label: 'Of Indian women who can name even one perimenopause symptom' },
        ].map(s => (
          <div class="stat-block">
            <div class="stat-big"><span class="stat-n">{s.num}</span>{s.unit && <span class="stat-u">{s.unit}</span>}</div>
            <div class="stat-l">{s.label}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── THE SILENCE IN INDIA ── -->
  <section class="silence-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="silence-inner">
        <div class="silence-quote-block">
          <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
          <blockquote>
            Beta, it's just your age. Everyone goes through it. Don't make it a big deal.
          </blockquote>
          <cite>— What too many Indian women are told</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="silence-content">
          <span class="label-dark">The reality in India</span>
          <h2>We don't talk about this.<br/>And that has a cost.</h2>
          <p>
            In India, perimenopause is invisible. There's barely a word for it in most of our languages.
            Women suffer through it — often for <strong>5 to 10 years</strong> — thinking they are depressed,
            "difficult," or simply falling apart.
          </p>
          <p>
            Doctors dismiss it. Families don't understand it. Women feel too ashamed to even name it.
          </p>
          <p class="silence-call">
            <strong>The Second Spring exists to break that silence.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── WHAT IS PERIMENOPAUSE ── -->
  <section class="section white" id="what-is-this">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="what-inner">
        <div class="what-text">
          <span class="label">What is this?</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Perimenopause — the chapter no one prepared you for</h2>
          <p class="body-text">
            Perimenopause is the years leading up to menopause — when your hormones begin to shift.
            It can start as early as your <strong>late 30s</strong> and last anywhere from 4 to 12 years.
          </p>
          <p class="body-text">
            It's not menopause. It's the transition. And it's real, it's physical, and it affects
            nearly every system in your body — your sleep, your mood, your memory, your periods,
            your skin, your heart.
          </p>
          <p class="body-text">
            This is not stress. This is not "ageing gracefully." This is biology — and you deserve
            to understand it.
          </p>
          <div class="what-facts">
            {[
              { num: '1 in 2', text: 'women experience significant perimenopause symptoms' },
              { num: '47', text: 'average age perimenopause is in full effect — but it can start at 35' },
              { num: '34+', text: 'recognised symptoms — many you\'d never connect to hormones' },
            ].map(f => (
              <div class="fact-row">
                <div class="fact-num">{f.num}</div>
                <div class="fact-text">{f.text}</div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="what-visual">
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <div class="timeline-title">Your hormonal journey</div>
            {[
              { phase: 'Reproductive years', range: '20s – late 30s', active: false },
              { phase: 'Perimenopause', range: 'Late 30s – early 50s', active: true, note: '← You might be here' },
              { phase: 'Menopause', range: '12 months without a period', active: false },
              { phase: 'Postmenopause', range: 'The rest of your life', active: false },
            ].map(t => (
              <div class={`timeline-item ${t.active ? 'active' : ''}`}>
                <div class="timeline-phase">{t.phase}</div>
                <div class="timeline-range">{t.range}</div>
                {t.note && <div class="timeline-note">{t.note}</div>}
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── SYMPTOMS ── -->
  <section class="section cream" id="symptoms">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="label">Common experiences</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Does any of this feel familiar?</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          These are not personality flaws. Not laziness. Not weakness. They are symptoms —
          and they have a name.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="symptom-grid">
        {[
          { emoji: '😤', label: 'Sudden anger & irritability',   desc: 'Snapping at people you love. Feeling unlike yourself. Wondering what is wrong with you.' },
          { emoji: '🌙', label: 'Sleepless nights',              desc: 'Waking at 2am, 3am, 4am — mind racing, body restless, exhausted all day.' },
          { emoji: '🔥', label: 'Hot flashes & night sweats',    desc: 'Waves of heat that soak through you — sometimes in the middle of meetings or meals.' },
          { emoji: '🧠', label: 'Brain fog & forgetfulness',     desc: 'Forgetting words. Losing your train of thought. Feeling like your mind isn\'t your own.' },
          { emoji: '📅', label: 'Irregular or heavy periods',    desc: 'Cycles changing, becoming unpredictable, heavier, lighter, or disappearing altogether.' },
          { emoji: '💔', label: 'Anxiety & low mood',            desc: 'A heaviness that has no clear cause. Worrying more. Crying more. Feeling disconnected.' },
          { emoji: '🤝', label: 'Relationship changes',          desc: 'Distance with your partner, feeling unseen, or struggling with intimacy in new ways.' },
          { emoji: '⚡', label: 'Low energy & joint pain',       desc: 'Tired despite sleeping. Aching joints. Feeling decades older than you should.' },
        ].map(s => (
          <a href="/chat" class="symptom-card">
            <span class="symptom-emoji">{s.emoji}</span>
            <span class="symptom-label">{s.label}</span>
            <span class="symptom-desc">{s.desc}</span>
            <span class="symptom-cta">Talk about this →</span>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── WHO IT'S FOR ── -->
  <section class="section white" id="who">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="label">Who is The Second Spring for?</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">This space was made for you</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="who-grid">
        {[
          {
            emoji: '🌸',
            title: 'Indian women in their 30s, 40s, and 50s',
            desc: 'You\'ve noticed something shifting — in your body, your mind, your emotions. You\'ve googled it at midnight. You\'ve wondered if you\'re alone in this. You\'re not.',
            cta: 'Start talking →',
          },
          {
            emoji: '💑',
            title: 'Husbands and partners',
            desc: 'The woman you love seems different. You want to support her but you don\'t know how. Understanding what she\'s going through is the most loving thing you can do right now.',
            cta: 'Understand her experience →',
          },
          {
            emoji: '👩‍👧',
            title: 'Adult daughters',
            desc: 'Your mother has changed — she\'s more emotional, forgetful, or withdrawn. You want to understand her and be there for her, but you don\'t know where to start.',
            cta: 'Understand your mum →',
          },
        ].map(w => (
          <div class="who-card">
            <div class="who-emoji">{w.emoji}</div>
            <h3 class="who-title">{w.title}</h3>
            <p class="who-desc">{w.desc}</p>
            <a href="/chat" class="who-link">{w.cta}</a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── HOW IT WORKS ── -->
  <section class="section green-section" id="how-it-works">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header light">
        <span class="label-light">Simple, private, warm</span>
        <h2 class="section-title light-text">How The Second Spring works</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle light-sub">No forms. No login. No judgement. Just a conversation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="steps-row">
        {[
          {
            icon: '💬',
            step: '01',
            title: 'You share what\'s on your mind',
            desc: 'Choose from common experiences, or just type what you\'re feeling. There\'s no wrong way to begin.',
          },
          {
            icon: '🌿',
            step: '02',
            title: 'Your companion listens first',
            desc: 'Before explaining anything, your companion makes you feel heard. Warm, real, no medical jargon.',
          },
          {
            icon: '🌸',
            step: '03',
            title: 'You get clarity — and a next step',
            desc: 'Understand what\'s happening, what to ask your doctor, or connect with a specialist when you\'re ready.',
          },
        ].map(s => (
          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-top">
              <span class="step-number">{s.step}</span>
              <span class="step-icon-text">{s.icon}</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="step-title">{s.title}</h3>
            <p class="step-desc">{s.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div class="steps-cta">
        <a href="/chat" class="btn btn-peach btn-lg">Open your companion →</a>
        <p class="steps-note">Free · Private · No sign-up · Available right now</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── VOICES ── -->
  <section class="section cream voices-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="label">You are not alone</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">What Indian women are saying</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="voices-grid">
        {[
          { quote: "I thought I was going mad. I cried for no reason, couldn't sleep, forgot words mid-sentence. My doctor said it was stress. It wasn't — it was perimenopause.", name: "Priya, 44", city: "Bengaluru" },
          { quote: "Nobody in my family had ever used the word 'perimenopause'. I didn't even know it existed until I was already two years into it.", name: "Kavitha, 47", city: "Chennai" },
          { quote: "My husband thought I had become 'difficult'. I thought so too. Having a place to finally understand what was happening changed everything.", name: "Meena, 43", city: "Mumbai" },
        ].map(v => (
          <div class="voice-card">
            <div class="voice-quote-mark">"</div>
            <p class="voice-text">{v.quote}</p>
            <div class="voice-attr">
              <span class="voice-name">{v.name}</span>
              <span class="voice-city">{v.city}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      <p class="voices-note">These reflect common experiences shared with us. Names changed for privacy.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── ABOUT / FOUNDER ── -->
  <section class="section white founder-section" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="founder-inner">
        <div class="founder-photo-col">
          <div class="founder-photo">
            <img src="/rudra.jpg" alt="Rudra Kasturi — Founder, The Second Spring" />
          </div>
          <div class="founder-badge">Founder</div>
          <div class="founder-links">
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/rudrakasturi" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="founder-link">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6zM2 9h4v12H2z"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg>
              LinkedIn
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.rudrakasturi.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="founder-link">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
              Website
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="founder-content">
          <span class="label">The person behind this</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Rudra Kasturi</h2>
          <p class="founder-text">
            Rudra shapes the strategic direction and technology foundation that powers The Second Spring.
            A seasoned technology leader and entrepreneur, he brings deep experience in building digital
            products at scale — and a conviction that technology should make healthcare more human, not less.
          </p>
          <p class="founder-text">
            At The Second Spring, Rudra leads product, engineering, and AI strategy — ensuring every feature
            is grounded in real clinical understanding and designed to give women faster, clearer,
            and more compassionate care.
          </p>
          <p class="founder-text">
            The idea was personal. Watching the women closest to him navigate perimenopause with no language,
            no support, and no recognition of what they were experiencing — that became the reason this exists.
          </p>
          <div class="founder-name">
            <strong>Rudra Kasturi</strong>
            <span>Founder &amp; CEO, The Second Spring</span>
          </div>
          <a href="mailto:hello@thesecondspring.com" class="btn btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── FINAL CTA ── -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-inner">
        <div class="cta-leaf">🌿</div>
        <h2 class="cta-title">
          You don't have to figure this out alone.
        </h2>
        <p class="cta-desc">
          Thousands of Indian women are going through exactly what you're experiencing right now.
          Start a private conversation — no login, no judgement, no cost.
        </p>
        <a href="/chat" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Begin your Second Spring →</a>
        <p class="cta-fine">Information only — not medical advice. Always consult your doctor for personal health decisions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(150deg, #0F2A1A 0%, #1A3D2B 40%, #2A5C45 100%);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 7rem 0 6rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg-shapes { position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; }
  .shape {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: .12;
  }
  .shape-1 {
    width: 600px; height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #D4845A, transparent);
    right: -150px; top: -150px;
  }
  .shape-2 {
    width: 400px; height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #7FB89A, transparent);
    left: -100px; bottom: -100px;
  }
  .shape-3 {
    width: 200px; height: 200px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #FBBF81, transparent);
    left: 55%; top: 60%;
  }
  .hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 700px; }
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: .5rem;
    font-size: .78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.8);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);
    padding: .4rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5.5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.12;
    letter-spacing: -.035em;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }
  .hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: #FBBF81; }
  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1.12rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.82);
    line-height: 1.78;
    max-width: 580px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2.25rem; }
  .hero-trust {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.75rem;
    font-size: .86rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.6);
  }

  /* ── STATS STRIP ── */
  .stats-strip {
    background: #0F2A1A;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
    padding: 2.5rem 0;
  }
  .stats-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
  }
  .stat-block {
    padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-block:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .stat-big {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: .2rem;
    margin-bottom: .4rem;
  }
  .stat-n {
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--peach);
    letter-spacing: -.03em;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-u {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--peach);
    opacity: .8;
  }
  .stat-l {
    font-size: .78rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.55);
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 160px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ── VOICES ── */
  .voices-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.75rem;
  }
  .voice-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .voice-quote-mark {
    font-size: 4rem;
    line-height: .8;
    color: var(--peach);
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    opacity: .4;
    margin-bottom: .5rem;
  }
  .voice-text {
    font-size: .94rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .voice-attr {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: .75rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }
  .voice-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: .88rem; color: var(--text); }
  .voice-city { font-size: .82rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .voices-note {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: .78rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── FOUNDER LINKS ── */
  .founder-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: .75rem;
    margin-top: .25rem;
  }
  .founder-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: .4rem;
    font-size: .82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--green);
    background: var(--green-light);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    padding: .4rem .85rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    transition: all .18s;
  }
  .founder-link:hover {
    background: var(--green);
    color: #fff;
    border-color: var(--green);
  }

  /* ── SILENCE SECTION ── */
  .silence-section {
    background: #0F2A1A;
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }
  .silence-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .silence-quote-block {
    position: relative;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }
  .quote-mark {
    font-size: 5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--peach);
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    margin-bottom: -.5rem;
    opacity: .7;
  }
  blockquote {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.88);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  cite {
    font-size: .85rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.45);
    font-style: normal;
  }
  .silence-content { color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); }
  .label-dark {
    display: inline-flex;
    font-size: .76rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--peach);
    background: rgba(212,132,90,.15);
    padding: .3rem .85rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: .85rem;
  }
  .silence-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -.025em;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .silence-content p {
    font-size: .97rem;
    line-height: 1.78;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.7);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .silence-call {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.9) !important;
    font-size: 1.05rem !important;
    padding-top: .5rem;
  }

  /* ── WHAT IS THIS ── */
  .what-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .body-text { font-size: .97rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.78; margin-bottom: 1.1rem; }
  .what-facts { margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
  .fact-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }
  .fact-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .fact-num {
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--peach);
    white-space: nowrap;
    min-width: 80px;
    letter-spacing: -.02em;
  }
  .fact-text { font-size: .88rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5; }

  .timeline-card {
    background: var(--green-light);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 1.75rem;
    position: sticky;
